          Accounting platform for managing transactions within bank accounts, perfect for small businesses and charities.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-0.5">
        <a
          href="https://captivate.prossermedia.co.uk"
          class="underline font-medium hover:text-zinc-200 transition inline-flex"
          >Captivate</a
        >
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-6">
          An all-in-one learning platform for students &mdash; including
          flashcards, note-taking and question practise for Maths, Chemistry and
          Physics at A-Level (currently).
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-0.5">
        <p class="font-medium inline-flex">Forks</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-6">
          Modern recipe manager with built-in support for meal planning.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-0.5">
        <a
          href="https://myhandymandarren.com"
          class="underline font-medium hover:text-zinc-200 transition inline-flex"
          >My Handyman Darren</a
        >
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-6">
          Simple website for a handyman business.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-0.5">
        <p class="font-medium inline-flex">Wilcrick Forge</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-6">
          Website for a website for a small business offering farriery services
          advertising its services.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-0.5">
        <p class="font-medium inline-flex">Party for a Princess</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-6">
          Website for a small party business.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-0.5">
        <p class="font-medium inline-flex">The Fairy Project</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-6">
          Website for a client aiming to showcase hand made wild nature art
          sculptures.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
